data.description: This charming Cape Cod single-family home has been thoughtfully upgraded and impeccably maintained, and offers everything you need for comfortable living. With 3 bedrooms, 1 ½ bathrooms, and a spacious basement with an additional kitchen and 1/2 bath, there's plenty of room for everyone. The home has been recently updated with fresh paint, new fixtures, and newer appliances. Enjoy peace of mind with surveillance equipment, vinyl flooring, and newer energy-efficient windows installed in 2022. Relax and unwind in the newly fenced-in backyard, perfect for barbecues and family gatherings. Schedule a viewing today and make this your dream home a reality!
